"       Patient information: Disease modifying antirheumatic drugs (DMARDs) (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/5/16466?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Discoid lupus (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
