"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/42/36518?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Systemic lupus erythematosus and pregnancy (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
